test_PCP<- read_excel("E:/COSAS DE OSCAR DEFINITIVO/OSCAR/2020-2/Proyecto- PAPA/ANOMALIAS/ANOMALIAS POR CLUSTER/entrada pror departamento/boyaca/C0/PCP_boy_C0.xlsx", 
    sheet = "Hoja2")
test_PCP
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
library(zoo)
library(ggfortify)
library(forecast)

tmed.ts=ts(test$prom,start = 1981,frequency = 12)
arima_tmed<-auto.arima(tmed.ts)
forecast_tmed<-forecast(arima_tmed,level = c(95), h = 60)
PCP.ts=ts(test_PCP$prom,start = 1981,frequency = 12)
arima_PCP<-auto.arima(PCP.ts)
forecast_PCP<-forecast(arima_PCP,level = c(95), h = 60)

pgreen4_tmed_C1=autoplot(forecast_tmed)+xlab("Año")+ylab("Temperatura media [°C]")+ggtitle("Pronostico Temperatura media C1 - Boyacá",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2025")

pgreen4_PCP_C1=autoplot(forecast_PCP)+xlab("Año")+ylab("Precipitacion [mm]")+ggtitle("Precipitacion C1 - Boyacá",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2025")

pgreen4_tmed_C1

pgreen4_PCP_C1


año=c(2021:2025)
meses=c("año","enero","febrero","marzo","abril","mayo","junio","julio","agosto","septiembre","octubre","noviembre","diciembre")
tmed_fut=matrix(forecast_tmed$mean)
tmed_fut=matrix(tmed_fut,12,5)
tmed_fut=data.frame(año,t(tmed_fut))
names(tmed_fut)=meses
tmed_fut
PCP_fut=matrix(forecast_PCP$mean)
PCP_fut=matrix(PCP_fut,12,5)
PCP_fut=data.frame(año,t(PCP_fut))
names(PCP_fut)=meses
PCP_fut

write.csv(tmed_fut,"tmed_fut_C1_boy.csv")
write.csv(PCP_fut,"PCP_fut_C1_boy.csv")

p_tmed_1=autoplot(tmed_1)+xlab("Año")+ylab("Temperatura media [°C]")+ggtitle("Temperatura media C1 - Boyacá del mes: Enero",subtitle = "Periodo 2021-2025 Fase: Senescencia y Cosecha")+ geom_line(aes(y=tmed_1,colour="T. media °C"))  + geom_line(aes(y=16,colour="T. min Verticillium °C"))+ scale_colour_manual("", values=c("T. media °C"="black", "T. min Verticillium °C"="green4"))
